asset.hookText:
http://odyssey.tagheuer.com - The Odyssey of Pioneers is now in Asia. Enjoy the beautiful scenery of India while the Odyssey arrives in New Delhi, before attending a cocktail hosted by the Maharaja of Jaipur himself. Among the attendees were TAG Heuer CEO Jean-Christophe Babin and TAG Heuer ambassador Karun Chandok.
